{"tid":306582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"上通識堂會唔會唔習慣","createTime":"2017-07-02T15:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T16:18:30.000Z","uid":90370,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c54a5bf0c2ef57c08a9128e866e6d86b8a669ed9","tid":306582,"uid":90370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T15:59:58.000Z","msg":"上黎高登ㄧ段日子，發現大家政治議題上對於不同意見既包容性唔係咁大，反而排他性就一啲都唔低，ㄧ見到有人以較為保守既出發點看待事情往往會極力攻擊同貶低對方，甚至唔提出任何實質證據就指控對方係五毛。當大家上通識堂既時候必定會接觸到林林總總、五花百門既觀點，當中有部分源於較為保守既出發點。試問你地有冇覺得唔習慣甚至唔舒服？"},{"pid":"75f3120dffd30ee15ea1824da321de26d79ad6fb","tid":306582,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:16:30.000Z","msg":"你係咪上錯科林<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3a65b17d6a176349fb7481b65700d6134a785af","tid":306582,"uid":118551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T16:18:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}